## ðŸš€ Getting Started

### Clone the repo
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/smart-devops-dashboard.git
cd smart-devops-dashboard
```

### Setup Backend
```bash
cd server
npm install
npm run dev
```

### Setup Frontend
```bash
cd client
npm install
npm start
```

### Run (Optional) ML Service
```bash
cd ml-service
pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py
```

### Docker Compose (Full Stack)
```bash
docker-compose up --build
```

